title: PLEASE HELP IMPORTANT
body: Still not loading after champ select tried lots of times and I got a low priority queue {{champion:122}}

replies.body:
I think this is something we can definitely help get rid of and solve!  But first, I need a bit more information:

What happens after you get out of Champion Select exactly?  Do you get an error?  Does the Loading Screen never appear?  

Reply back and let me know!

thanks for the reply fam. reinstall seems to have fixed it.  rip my low priority queue. guess there's no way to prove it {{item:3070}}  but yea the loading screen never appeared and there was no error.

Glad to hear that a re-install seemed to fix the issue! :)  Once you get past the Low Priority Queue, you should be all set!

Feel free to make another thread if you experience any other types of issues!
